collection.name: Jadu Jetpack
collection.description:
Upcoming Airdrop: [Jadu AVA](https://twitter.com/JaduAVAs/status/1526618896085622785?s=20&t=Lr7aZCASKGGoJCkFc4DLoQ) • 2nd Collection: [Jadu Hoverboards](https://opensea.io/collection/jadu-hoverboard) • 30% [Staked](https://twitter.com/JaduAVAs/status/1527367742948421644?s=20&t=_aytvHCnIZ3Ko3d-qZc9_A)

Designed to allow your avatar to fly in AR, Jetpacks were a rare instance of an NFT game object showcasing true interoperability and permissionlessness.

Today this simple 3D Jetpack represents the cutting edge of AR and Web3. It provides its holders a front row seat to the making of the Mirrorverse.

Signature Series: Trippy
